 jingle, you know, only - well perhaps would seat four each side. And some of them would seat six each side.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Which way would the seats be facing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Facing one another, you know, long - sort of long}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12266206\charrsid12073373  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 ways, like - just like a jingle would be, what we call the jingle. A jingle see, you seat perhaps two or three couldn't you each side, well these were - suit - I suppose four or five cou}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241735\charrsid12073373 ld sit in a seat of - the break}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 . Then of course - a bigger party would go in a Jersey car.
