No. Horse drawn. Mm. I remember mother used to take part - well that was the 14/18 war - they used to come in here and serve meals. You know - in the church hall there they used to - the - now there was}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6241735\charrsid12073373  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 a lot of women I know in Poo
l - used to come down and serve meals. Get meals ready for schoolchildren. Then soup and that sort of thing. And then they used to have a working party knitting you know socks and one thing and another for the forces, and they used to have two or three ou
tings a year. And I remember going off with mother in a Jersey car to - to - Godrevy and all those places you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 That would be closed, would have a top on it?
