ry hay and all on. I think that's what they called it and - they used to put - well of course - I think there are some - that Mr Stewart from Treleigh has got some Jersey cars now I think, or he's got a Jersey car I think that he - goes to these - differe
nt to-does you know with }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241735\charrsid12073373 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373  horse}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241735\charrsid12073373 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 drawn things.
