Oh yes, she used to do her share like you know, any - anything social - attached to the Conservative party she would help but she wouldn't take part in politics you know, not - outside or anything like that,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 She would have held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Because your father did?
