\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 
That's right, I've heard father talk about old Conybeare 'cos they had - there was a song about old Conybeare and - I always remember father te
lling about Conybeare you know. Then there was Mr Dunn wasn't it. He was at Portreath then. He was the Liberal I think. I think he was the Liberal man wasn't he, Mr Dunn. Then there was - Moreing, when was he there. Captain Moreing was it, He married Miss
 Ormond. Yes. Yes. Yes, no I don't remember - much about - you know, that sort of thing then.
