Yes, oh - and the dust that that made you know. And when it came - to the oven taking out - that was another dirty job. And there was fires going all the time then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Coal fires?
