No, had her regular once a week she'd come. Sometimes she would do one job, perhaps the stove didn't want a big clean every week but - you know, it used to be done, 'cos that - mother was - that was a great pride of hers. Oh - all the brass}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11157569\charrsid12073373 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 
work on it, you know, this rack and the oven door was beaut - you know, beautiful - stove it was, everybody admired it. And of course it was well used. 'Cos all the cooking was done that way then.
