Oh yes. She was - yes, she was never very well, you know, I can always remember her - her looking back spasms of poorliness you know which I didn't understand much abou
t then, and then after I got married she had to have a - she was in hospital, she had a serious operation then, in hospital, she was in Redruth nursing home for - for five or six weeks. I wasn't - well - married just a month or two and we went up to look 
after fathe - then and slept and - sort of lived up there, shut up here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 When she was ill did this lady used to come then?
