ping Forest, and I remember going to London to stay and staying with them. She was from Penzance. She was called Williams and they used to come - she had two little girls then, and - we used to go there and stay at - in London, you know, used to go up the
n
 in those days. And I remember going to - well Shepherds Bush then you know to - the big to do there, I always remember that, and going to Westminister Abbey, that will always stand in my mind, you know and - we were took - went round quite a lot we did t
here, four of us went I know. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Mother, father you and your brother?
