\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No. See the long silk dresses then they we}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11157569\charrsid12073373 
