oming up from St Ives - you know, mother's relatives from there, yes. She used to have a - Miss Curnow, she was the headmistress in Halsetown school, and mother used to go to a Mrs Penberuthy's school in - Halsetown, used to pay three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
