 - I've heard her say, this little school, and there was - that's right, yes, and - Sir Henry Irving lived there, and - it's funny, my husband's family are - are - they're descendants of the - Sir Henry Irving, and it was funny when mother used to tell th
e story to my husband his father and they went back you know and - you could see it was all coupled up - the same - yes, that's right, yes. Yes.
