sed to go to Camborne School of Mines then, we went there for a while, evening class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 You're interested in art?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Well I was then, you know, but - then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 This was for painting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes. Yes. And then the war came on see and all those things were squashed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 
No. Not now, you know, I think - I used to think sometimes well - I wish I did - take more interest perhaps and - went on further but still - I didn't have much time to do anything else afterwards 'cos I - busy all the time since.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11157569\charrsid12073373 Do you think you benefi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 ted from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 
Oh yes, funny I was only saying to Arthur her - when he was here a fortnight ago, I said, when you look about - what we were taught in those days h
ow it was grounded in then, we shan't forget it. He said, when you look at education now the way that - oh he said it makes your blood boil you know and these education committees now what's being done, and the money that's being wasted in a way. And he s
aid the Technical Colleges of course can get as much money as they want.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 While you were at school did you have a part job or any means of earning a little pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No. Nothing. No. Well used to fetch tobacco for an old man up Pool, he used t
o give me three ha'pence a fortnight. He had ounce a day. Westward Ho I know it was, and we used to go to - Saunders the shop then, and fetch this tobacco for this old chap, old Mr Roberts it was, and he used to give us three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11157569\charrsid12073373  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 ha'pence a fortnight for doing that, so that was the - spare - that was the - spare cash.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 How did you come to do that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 
Well, he was a grandpa to my friend you know. The girl I used to go around with - was her grandpa, and if she couldn't go I used to go. We used to sort of take it in turn. Three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11157569\charrsid12073373  }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 ha'pence a fortnight, yes. And we were thrilled over that too. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 I'd like to ask you about your first full time job, what was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Oh - that was at Climax. On munitions then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 That was working on munitions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 How old were you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Seventeen. And that was all I done - working at -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Well - we were told - we had to go out when we got a certain age you know, 'til we were eligible to go to work on munitions, I 
was home until then. Not doing anything, but we had to go out, you know, sort of compulsory then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 You were at home until what age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Seventeen - sixteen or seventeen, I think it was seventeen when were allowed out - to go - on munitions I think it
 was. So I had to go then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 That would have been in about 1916?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes. Yes, I should think so, about six - 1916. I've got diaries here you know from 1932. Kept every day. Since 1932.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 What hours did you work when you were on munitions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 We
 used to work three shifts. Morning, afternoon and night shift. Six to - six to - what was it, six to two. We used to go to work ten o'clock was it until eight - no, it couldn't have been ten o'clock to eight, ten to six in the morning. Then go in six o'c
lock until two. And two to ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you have to work Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No. I didn't.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 What about Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Saturday mornings. When we were on a certain shift, like morning shifte, we had to work Saturday mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No, I don't think we did then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Do you remember what you were paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No, I couldn't re - I don't remember now. Very little I know. Well compared to what it is now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you think it was a fair wage at the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Oh we thought it was a lot, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 I used to give it all to her you know. I used to keep - well she used to keep it and whatever I wanted I had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 What would it have been spent on, in the family money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes. Food and I suppose clothing when I wanted it you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 You'd have it back again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Oh yes, yes, I don't think I kept myself, not really. And then at that time - well - when I was getting money - she was b
uying a lot of linen and stuff you know - well preparing a bottom drawer, I've got lots of stuff now that she bought, table cloths and everything you know, before I was married, and pillowcases even that I've never used - or used you know, but they're not
 done yet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 How did you get on with the people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Oh very well. Very happy. -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 How did your employer treat you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Very well. He was a - a - Tom Letcher was there then, he was a relative of - my husband's, he was the head one
, yes. - Yes. And got on very well with all of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 How did you feel about the work itself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 
Oh it was all right. I didn't mind at all, I didn't like the - some of the shifts, you know, morning shift I didn't like at all. Getting up so early in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Was it heavy work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 
No. No. Although - well - what were they then, the - the shells were two - pounds and twenty-five pounds in the last war. What was ours, twelve pounds were they - shells we used to make, I used to put the copper b
ands on - on those you know. I remember doing that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Doing it with a machine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 That's it, and then I went on another job which we done six operations on one - machine you know. They were new ones then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Was it dangerous work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Well it could be for your hands you know, you could cut your hands easy with - with the sharp tools.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No explosives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Oh no. No. No was only machinery and steel work you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 You didn't dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Have you done any jobs since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 After you left school did you continue to live at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes. Until I got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you continue to spend your Sundays as before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Church and Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No. My husband was more of a Liberal. He - I - you know, I think - when there wasn't a Liberal candidate - he'd vote Conservative, b
ut he was more Liberal. He wasn't Labour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you continue to spend your spare time in the same way after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you go out of an evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Not very often. Perhaps twice a week. Courting nights was Tuesdays and Thursdays. Saturdays and Sundays very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 You'd go for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes. Well there was no cars there. That's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you make any new friends, boy or girls at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Well - like - you know, your girl friends, you got in with their boyfri
ends and that sort of thing, and like people that my husband worked with, got friendly with them, and their wives, or girls you know. And the girls you worked with and - of course he would know them as well. And - sort of his relatives around but - he did
n't have a lot of them but - he had lots of friends around, so - but we sort of - always thought who we were mixing with you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you ever bring friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you have any special friends at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Boys nor girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did they expect to know where you were if you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Well you - they sort of knew - where - you know, where I should be. Didn't go very far afield. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Oh father used to like us in early. Or, you know, sort of nine o'clock, if we weren't in by nine - he'd be looking at the clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 When your father was working as a postman, were uniforms supplied for them to wear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 
Oh yes, he had the full outfit you know with the peaked cap or peaked hat rather, and a full uniform and wouldn't - never allowed to wear anything else in his work then - in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Does that include shoes or boots?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 I think they ha
d an allowance for boots, but it was mostly heavy boots then that they wore, because they had to travel so - you know, so much. Light shoes weren't any good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 It was all walking wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 What age was Mr Andrew when he retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Sixty-five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 You were saying about the gas lamps at the markets when you were young, would those have been the gas lamps that flared?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14353856 MP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Yes. I c-making a terrible noise all round the stall you know, like - gales of wind coming in.
