\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13971602 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14365183\charrsid12073373 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among the workers at the ammunition factory?
